IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. EvalContracted.

DATA DIVISION.
01 X PICTURE IS 99.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
EVALUATE X
    WHEN 10 OR 20
        DISPLAY "EVALUATE CONTRACTED VALUES"
    WHEN 30 OR 40 OR 50
        DISPLAY "MULTIPLE OR"
    WHEN OTHER
        DISPLAY "NONE MATCHED"
END

EVALUATE X
    WHEN 10 THROUGH 20 OR 30 THROUGH 40
        DISPLAY "CONTRACTED THROUGH RANGES"
    WHEN OTHER
        DISPLAY "NO RANGE MATCH"
END

EVALUATE TRUE
    WHEN X > 5 AND X < 15 OR X > 25
        DISPLAY "CONTRACTED CONDITION"
END.